      <description>
        <p>
          <b>Test Data:</b>
        </p>
        <p>-</p>
        <p>
          <b>Steps to reproduce:</b>
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Create a User A.</li>
          <li>Create an Article using token of the User A.</li>
          <li>Create a User B.</li>
          <li>Try to delete ab Article of User A using token of the User A</li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          <b>Expected result:</b>
        </p>
        <p>Status code: 401 Unauthorized. Response body should contain an error indicating that the
          user is not allowed to delete the article.</p>
